profile: Homeology is a blog created for people to extend their imagination when deciding to choose the lighting for their homes. Inappropriate lighting can really bring an uneasy and not very welcoming feeling inside a house, that’s why Homeology explains in its blog posts how contemporary light fixtures can really brighten up the house as well as sharing the factors one should consider before buying such fixtures. Lighting solutions changes for every building but onion light fixtures can be incorporated into any space. With their rich history and versatility, this is one of the still going on strong picks from lighting stores and Homeology has an article explaining everything about it. Have you heard about Log homes? Well you can know about them in this blog where their origin, features, and benefits can be read about. Another interesting piece of information readers will find interesting is their piece on small house plans. With the rise in population and lack of space, apartments are now the only solution for many people who have learnt to live in a comparatively smaller area. Yet there are different types of small houses and you can learn more about them right here. To know more about home construction or home lighting, visit http://homeology.info/ and http://homeology.info/category/constructing-your-house/.
